  "description": "<p></p><p>Location: Caldecott/Novena</p><p>Salary: Up to $5,000</p><p>Working Hours:</p><p>Mon – Fri (9:00am – 6:00pm)</p><p>Sat (9:00am – 1:00pm)<br /><br /><br /></p><p></p><p>Job Scope</p><p>Provide nursing care to O&G patients in a hospital setting</p><p>Assist doctors during procedures, treatments, and consultations</p><p>Monitor patient progress and provide post-procedure care</p><p>Educate patients on treatment plans and recovery</p><p>Ensure compliance with nursing and safety standards</p><p><br /><br /><br /></p><p>Requirements</p><p>Minimum Diploma in Nursing; registered with Singapore Nursing Board</p><p>Prior O&G nursing experience</p><p><br /><br /><br /></p><p>If interested, please email me at biopharma@recruitexpress.com.sg or telegram @alexgohhl</p><p></p><p>➖</p><p>Alex Goh Hock Leong</p><p>(CEI.No: R1763413 l Recruit Express Pte Ltd (Healthcare & Life Science) | 99C4599)</p>",
